E%3D&h=7f2478db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361795%26refer%3D&h=ab5f745c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=361795&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母。<br />\nNowTV訪問一名811被捕人士，受訪者稱當日被捕時被警察弄至骨折，當時並沒有反抗，亦沒有即時送院，反而送至新屋嶺。<br />\n約5小時後，他終被送到北區醫院救治，醫生證明他受襲擊導致左邊閉合性肩關節前方脫位、閉合性肱骨近端四個部分都骨折，需要做緊急手術，鑲鈦金屬片及螺絲固定。<br />\n不過，有律師就稱，類似情況只能以民事向警方索償，警方需向法庭披露使用武力及槍彈的守則，讓警方濫用暴力的爭議交由法庭裁決，但難以追究刑責。"},{"pid":"7540e81c3056db3a8c6397b42031beb4946a99b9","tid":1546502,"uid":259541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"你都白撚痴,唔通你幫差佬含撚下次就唔打你呀"},{"pid":"647d17f3f73a65bb097238d62858a452daf24d3e","tid":1546502,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"唔會有人會搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341ac8a7e3666a0a27333965eb85f349affd1209","tid":1546502,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"攝張老豆搵仔人情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bf3308ca93af58ace6b5ba271874d498961fbd","tid":1546502,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正怕咩俾人恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f76756be43ceb8e7f7526ddb361e69d1d4dee0","tid":1546502,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:34:24.000Z","msg":"mon post狗收皮啦"},{"pid":"f913015577f281b58b76295db1db86091dfc1ed3","tid":1546502,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"送個紙紮公仔賀下佢<br />\n禮多人不怪"},{"pid":"377d73c99069764194498278e747450844401687","tid":1546502,"uid":294632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:34:29.0